window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Spooky and Joe are in a gaming reality where it is quickly becoming clear that it is quite real. They are forced to fight monsters, dungeons, and betrayal, but their greatest enemy might be denial. Both Joe and Spooky are now nearly immortal, but how will Joe react when the facts of the situation can no longer be denied? He may never see his late wife in the afterlife.</p> <p>How will Spooky deal with the changes within herself? Neither she nor her co-Champion have the option to become mere mortals again.</p> <p>Listen as Joe and Spooky continue to grow their capital in people, skills, equipment, and magic.</p>"; 
